Date: Sat, 9 May 2026 08:30:22 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Tentative fix for NVIDIA 470.256.02 driver for
 Linux-next-20260508 (part 1: drm_atomic_state -> drm_atomic_commit rename)

Created using:

rg -l drm_atomic_state | \
        xargs sed -i 's/drm_atomic_state/drm_atomic_commit/g; s/drm_atomic_commit_helper/drm_atomic_state_helper/g'

Plus a few trivial manual edits.
